♪ You are a stranger ♪

24:31.302 --> 24:34.070
♪ But you're a pal of mine ♪

24:34.172 --> 24:36.706
MAN: One of A.P.'s trips
took him

24:36.774 --> 24:39.208
to the African-American
community

24:39.276 --> 24:41.577
of Kingsport, Tennessee.

24:41.646 --> 24:45.381
And he met Lesley Riddle, and
they struck up a friendship,

24:45.449 --> 24:50.419
and he asked Lesley to go out
and find more songs with him.

24:50.487 --> 24:52.823
I can't imagine what it was like

24:52.890 --> 24:57.126
for a white guy and a black guy
to go collecting.

25:10.641 --> 25:12.976
FLEMONS: They traveled together
for 10 years.

25:13.043 --> 25:15.145
And so A.P. would collect
the words,

25:15.213 --> 25:17.481
