25:32.764 --> 25:34.932
♪ I can see my baby ♪

25:34.999 --> 25:36.900
♪ Peepin' through the bars ♪

25:36.968 --> 25:39.035
BULGER: They were just like
sponges.

25:39.103 --> 25:42.638
They took Tin Pan Alley songs,
they took sheet music songs

25:42.707 --> 25:45.508
that people would have been
singing around the parlor,

25:45.576 --> 25:49.279
gospel songs,
shape note songs.

25:49.347 --> 25:51.714
You name it, they took it.

25:51.782 --> 25:54.851
CHARLES WOLFE: A.P. would go out
and collect these songs

25:54.919 --> 25:57.553
and write them down
on scraps of paper.

25:57.589 --> 26:00.389
And when he would come home
from one of his trips,

26:00.457 --> 26:02.825
he would unload his pockets,

26:02.894 --> 26:06.363
and he'd just pull out all these
scraps of envelopes and papers.

26:06.430 --> 26:10.367
And he would show these songs
to Sara and then to Maybelle,

26:10.434 --> 26:13.169
and then the next stage
would begin.

26:13.237 --> 26:16.973
They would shorten lines,
they would add beats,

26:17.041 --> 26:20.110
they would work out
a guitar accompaniment.

26:20.177 --> 26:23.813
So it was a wonderful
mini-production line,

26:23.881 --> 26:27.450
and A.P. was the great arranger.

26:27.452 --> 26:29.986
The Carter Family,
they were the performers

26:30.053 --> 26:32.856
and they were the ones who made
the popular records,

26:32.923 --> 26:36.526
and they made the money on the
records along with Ralph Peer,

26:36.594 --> 26:39.328
and Lesley Riddle didn't really
make any money.

26:39.397 --> 26:44.166
And we don't know if
Lesley Riddle was bitter over it

26:44.234 --> 26:46.569
or if he was okay with it.

26:46.637 --> 26:49.706
It's always hard to tell
what the intentions are

26:49.774 --> 26:53.209
around this sort of swapping
of music.

26:53.277 --> 26:55.779
But a lot of times
the story is that

26:55.846 --> 26:58.581
you have this popular
white performer,

26:58.649 --> 27:01.117
but there's a black person
in the background

27:01.185 --> 27:03.620
in every one of the scenes
almost.

27:03.688 --> 27:05.856
And just acknowledging
that they're there,

27:05.923 --> 27:07.891
that's a very important thing.

27:07.959 --> 27:09.659
