RADIO ANNOUNCER: In other words,
this is Station XET Monterrey,

29:40.144 --> 29:42.178
down Mexico way.

29:42.246 --> 29:44.714
Border radio refers to

29:44.781 --> 29:47.383
super high-powered
radio stations

29:47.451 --> 29:49.752
that were built
on the Mexican side

29:49.821 --> 29:54.057
of the U.S.-Mexican border
by outlaw broadcasters

29:54.125 --> 29:56.860
who went foul of the
Federal Radio Commission

29:56.928 --> 30:00.330
and had their license removed
and had to go somewhere

30:00.397 --> 30:05.101
to get around U.S. government
regulations about broadcasting.

30:05.168 --> 30:09.172
One of the first people
to have his license removed

30:09.240 --> 30:13.276
was a gentleman by the name
of Dr. John R. Brinkley,

30:13.344 --> 30:16.112
the "big daddy" of border radio.

30:16.180 --> 30:19.849
In the early 1920s, Dr. Brinkley
perfected an operation

30:19.917 --> 30:23.420
that I like to call
an early version of Viagra.

30:23.487 --> 30:25.054
And what Dr. Brinkley did

30:25.122 --> 30:28.557
was he took a small slice
of a goat gonad

30:28.625 --> 30:33.662
and inserted it into
a man's personal area.

30:33.730 --> 30:36.065
He did many, many
of these operations

30:36.133 --> 30:38.667
on many famous people
all around the world.

30:38.735 --> 30:41.337
So Dr. Brinkley made
a fortune.

30:41.405 --> 30:44.574
Well, Dr. Brinkley eventually
had his license removed

30:44.642 --> 30:47.310
for his questionable
medical practices.

30:47.378 --> 30:50.714
So Dr. Brinkley moved
to Del Rio, Texas,

30:50.781 --> 30:52.616
this little community
down on the border,

30:52.683 --> 30:55.452
and started up the station XERA

30:55.519 --> 30:57.954
across the Rio Grande
in old Mexico

30:58.021 --> 30:59.656
in the little town
of Villa Acuña.

30:59.724 --> 31:03.627
So he was outside all of
the regulations of the FRC.

31:03.728 --> 31:05.862
He could broadcast on any power
he wanted to,

31:05.929 --> 31:07.997
and he could say anything
he wanted to.

31:08.065 --> 31:11.133
Women, many of them,
are cold and frigid

31:11.201 --> 31:16.372
due to the fact that
their clitoris is hooded

31:16.440 --> 31:18.575
and needs un-hooding,

31:18.642 --> 31:21.444
which I call a circumcision
of a woman.

31:21.512 --> 31:23.813
It's a minor little affair,

31:23.881 --> 31:26.783
and properly done, as we do it
here in our hospital,

31:26.851 --> 31:29.319
it exposes the clitoris
to sensation.

31:29.386 --> 31:33.490
[ ♪♪ ]

31:47.838 --> 31:51.241
CRAWFORD: Radio was just
beginning to prove its worth

31:51.308 --> 31:52.975
as an advertising medium,

31:53.043 --> 31:55.945
and border radio was
like a magnet

31:56.013 --> 31:59.015
for broadcasting and
entertaining weirdos

31:59.082 --> 32:01.917
who would come and try
to sell things on the air.

32:01.985 --> 32:05.188
They were the first ones
to let preachers on the air

32:05.256 --> 32:06.789
to ask for money.

32:06.857 --> 32:09.325
They sold medicines,
they told fortunes.

32:09.392 --> 32:12.128
They sold "genuine simulated
diamonds."

32:12.196 --> 32:16.132
Another product was autographed
pictures of Jesus Christ.

32:16.200 --> 32:18.100
In addition, you had musicians.

32:18.169 --> 32:20.670
You had yodeling cowboys
and singing cowboys.

32:20.737 --> 32:23.906
You had Bob Wills,
the Father of Western Swing.

32:23.974 --> 32:27.910
They were the first ones to
really popularize country music.

32:27.978 --> 32:30.846
So it was like a psychic
country-western

32:30.914 --> 32:34.450
medicine show circus
24 hours a day.

32:34.518 --> 32:36.586
One of the biggest sellers
of medicines

32:36.653 --> 32:38.521
was a guy named Harry O'Neill.

32:38.589 --> 32:41.790
And he's selling Peruna:
guaranteed to help boost

32:41.858 --> 32:44.227
your cold-fighting,
cold-chasing ability.

32:44.294 --> 32:46.596
So he looks around America
to try to find

32:46.663 --> 32:50.166
the people who will appeal
to his clientele.

32:50.234 --> 32:52.635
ANNOUNCER: Let me introduce you
to the original Carter Family:

32:52.702 --> 32:55.938
A.P., Sara, Maybelle, Janette,
Helen, June, and Anita.

32:56.006 --> 33:00.409
[ Carter Family's
"Keep On the Sunny Side" plays ]

